snippet.title: SNES Kirby no Omochabako: Cannon Ball
snippet.description:
https://www.facebook.com/ShiryuVideoGames/

Dumped and preserved thanks to the efforts of Frank Cifaldi and Matthew Callis. "Kirby no Omocharo" (translated as "Kirby's Toy box") is a Sattelaview mini game collections. This is "Cannon Ball", a one or two player artillery style game. Enjoy!

More information: https://satellaview.org/
